      <title>摩根大通期望对其DEI政策批评</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/jpmorgan-expects-criticism-over-its-dei-policy-2025-02-14/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据周五的监管文件，摩根大通（JPMorgan Chase）预计将对其某些商业惯例（包括多样性，公平与包容）（DEI）面临批评。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/jpmorgan-expects-criticism-over-its-dei-policy-2025-02-14/</guid>
